embed.title: 🎫 Need Help? We're Here for You!
embed.description:
If you're experiencing an issue, need support, or want to talk to the team privately, you can open a confidential support ticket by clicking the button below.

🛡️ Your privacy is our priority – only you and our support team will be able to view the conversation inside your ticket.

✅ Use this system for:
• Questions or general help
• Reporting issues or bugs
• Private conversations with staff
• Any other support-related needs

📌 To open a ticket, simply click the Create Ticket button below. A private channel will be created just for you.

📝 Once your ticket is open, please explain your situation clearly so we can help you as fast and efficiently as possible.
